headline: Move Over Skincare: Gen Z Is Obsessed With Aesthetic Oral Care And MySmile Is Leading the Glow-Up
summary: Skincare isn't the only beauty essential topping Gen Z's routines anymore. Oral care has officially joined the aesthetic revolution, and MySmile is the brand at the center of it. With TikTok and Instagram buzzing over whitening transformations, ultraclean bathroom shelfies, and chic dental kits, MySmile is rewriting what it means to care for your smile.

headline: Herbivore Debuts Exclusive Bodycare Collection and Partnership with Ulta Beauty
summary: Herbivore, the prestige, plant-powered beauty brand known for its thoughtful formulations, today announced a new partnership with Ulta Beauty, the nation's largest beauty retailer. As part of the rollout, Herbivore will debut a first-of-its-kind 15-piece Body Collection exclusively to Ulta Beauty, which will be available in over 850 stores nationwide starting December 28, 2025.

headline: 2 Unpopular Stocks That Deserve a Second Chance and 1 Facing Headwinds
summary: When Wall Street turns bearish on a stock, it’s worth paying attention. These calls stand out because analysts rarely issue grim ratings on companies for fear their firms will lose out in other business lines such as M&A advisory.
